    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_810-887",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "810-887",
      "markText": "皇亲国戚有犯，在嗣君自决。除谋逆不赦外，其余所犯，轻者与在京诸亲会议，重者与在外诸王及在京诸亲会议，皆取自上裁。其所犯之家，止许法司举奏，并不许擅自拿问。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=810&rangeEnd=887",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=810&rangeEnd=887"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_2906-2977",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2906-2977",
      "markText": "凡警备常用器械、衣甲，不离左右；更选良马数匹，调教能行速走者，常于宫门喂养。及四城门，令内使带鞍辔各置一匹，在其所在，一体上古帝王诸侯防御也。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2906&rangeEnd=2977",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2906&rangeEnd=2977"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_420-463",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "420-463",
      "markText": "其中奸顽刁诈之徒，情犯深重、灼然无疑者，特令法外加刑，意在使人知所警惧，不敢轻易犯法。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=420&rangeEnd=463",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=420&rangeEnd=463"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_3071-3101",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3071-3101",
      "markText": "凡帝王居宫，要早起睡迟，酒要少饮，饭要依时进，午后不许太饱。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3071&rangeEnd=3101",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3071&rangeEnd=3101"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_10_1752-1803",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1752-1803",
      "markText": "如朝无正臣，内有奸恶，则亲王训兵待命，天子密诏诸王，统领镇兵讨平之。既平之后，收兵于营，王朝天子而还。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1752&rangeEnd=1803",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1752&rangeEnd=1803"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_3524-3550",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3524-3550",
      "markText": "凡古王侯，妄窥大位者，无不自取灭亡，或连及朝廷俱废。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3524&rangeEnd=3550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3524&rangeEnd=3550"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_486-551",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "486-551",
      "markText": "以后子孙做皇帝时，止守律与大诰，并不许用黥刺、腓、劓、阉割之刑。云何？盖嗣君宫内生长，人情善恶，未能周知；恐一时所施不当，误伤善良",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=486&rangeEnd=551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=486&rangeEnd=551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_9_2584-2671",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2584-2671",
      "markText": "凡东宫、亲王位下、各拟名二十字。日后生子及孙，即以上闻，付宗人府。所立双名，每一世取一字以为上字；其下一字，临时随意选择，以为双名，编入玉牒。至二十世后，照例续添，永为定式。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2671",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2671"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_733-779",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "733-779",
      "markText": "以后子孙做皇帝时，并不许立丞相。臣下敢有奏请设立者，文武群臣即时劾奏，将犯人凌迟，全家处死。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129156&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=733&rangeEnd=779",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/30132c10813ab98f3g016dc8?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=733&rangeEnd=779"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129156_4_2772-2836",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2772-2836",
      "markText": "虽亲信如骨肉，朝夕相见，犹当警备于心，宁有备而无用。如欲回避左右，与亲信人密谋国事，其常随内官及带刀人员止可离十丈地，不可太远。",
